nd may explain\nthe errors of PZ SIC for equilibrium properties, opening the door to a\ngeneralized SIC that is more widely accurate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jan 2019 22:50:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Apr 2019 17:01:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-26"}
