istribution of the chemical spots does not follow the magnetic field topology,\nwhich indicates that the role of the magnetic field in the creation and\nmaintenance of the surface structures may be more subsidiary than what is\npredicted by theoretical studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Feb 2019 13:51:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-20"}
