c to $\\Phi$ X for\nany commutative diagram X in A, then the range of $\\Phi$ is anti-elementary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Feb 2019 14:26:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 May 2019 12:23:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Sep 2020 07:18:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-03"}
